subject: Booking Extended — {{ booking_id }}
<h2>Rental Extension Confirmed</h2>
<p>Dear {{ customer_name }},</p>
<p>Your rental at {{ hub_name }} has been extended.</p>
<table>
  <tr><td><strong>Booking ID:</strong></td><td>{{ booking_id }}</td></tr>
  <tr><td><strong>New End Time:</strong></td><td>{{ new_end_time }}</td></tr>
  <tr><td><strong>Additional Charge:</strong></td><td>{{ additional_charge }}</td></tr>
</table>
<p>Please return the bike by the new return time to avoid further charges.</p>
